title: Dublin airport closed due to fire
text:
Dublin airport closed due to fire   
Aug 26, 2015 eTN   
The pilot is telling passengers Dublin airport will remain closed for the next 4 hrs. 
A Fire at DublinAirport in a restricted area separate from passenger facilities shut down operation Thursday morning. 
The fire alarm was triggered at about 07:15 local time. There are no reports of any injuries. 
The fire at Dublin Airport hangar has been contained but flight operations remain suspended
